      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide for the issuance of a forever stamp to honor the sacrifices of the brave men and women of the Armed Forces who are still prisoner, missing, or unaccounted for, and for other purposes.</title>
